            "heading": "Unique Nameplate",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>Discover the perfect way to celebrate your limited-edition e-bike with a nameplate, which showcases your e-bike's unique serial number and makes your e-bike truly one-of-a-kind!<br/></p>",
